# AI-Assistant — Mac configuration (example)
#
# Copy this file to mac/config.local.env (gitignored) and edit the lines
# that apply to your setup. Every setting is optional — anything you leave
# commented out falls back to the portable default shown beside it.
#
# Precedence (highest first):
#   1. Environment variable in the calling shell
#   2. mac/config.local.env (this file, after copy)
#   3. Hardcoded portable defaults
#
# Format is plain Bash KEY=VALUE — do not put spaces around the =. Quote
# any value that contains spaces, &, or other shell metacharacters.

# --- ComfyUI sidecar -------------------------------------------------------

# Path to your ComfyUI install. The default (~/ComfyUI) is the conventional
# Mac location and matches every ComfyUI tutorial out there.
#
# If you already have ComfyUI managed by Stability Matrix, point at it:
#   AI_ASSISTANT_COMFY_DIR="/Volumes/SSD/Stability Matrix/Data/Packages/ComfyUI"
#
# Default: $HOME/ComfyUI
#AI_ASSISTANT_COMFY_DIR="$HOME/ComfyUI"

# Python interpreter ComfyUI runs in. Auto-detected from the venv inside
# AI_ASSISTANT_COMFY_DIR (venv/bin/python or .venv/bin/python). Override
# only if you have multiple ComfyUI venvs and want to pin one.
#AI_ASSISTANT_COMFY_PYTHON=""

# HTTP port for the sidecar. Change if 8188 conflicts.
# Default: 8188
#AI_ASSISTANT_COMFY_PORT=8188

# Whether mac/install_comfyui.sh may clone ComfyUI on your behalf.
# Default is "false" so a missing install fails loud rather than silently
# downloading ~200 MB. Set to "true" to opt in:
#   AI_ASSISTANT_AUTO_CLONE=true ./mac/install_comfyui.sh
#
# Default: false
#AI_ASSISTANT_AUTO_CLONE=false

# --- ESRGAN upscaler -------------------------------------------------------

# Model name (filename) used for the high-res output upscale. Auto-engages
# only when the user requests an output larger than what we render at
# (typically the リサイズ tab).
#
# The default is 4x_NMKD-Superscale-SP_178000_G.pth, a general-purpose
# 4× upscaler that ships with Stability Matrix's default Models tree.
# Set to "" to disable ESRGAN entirely (LANCZOS fallback in the action).
# For anime/illustration-tuned upscalers swap in e.g.:
#   AI_ASSISTANT_UPSCALER="4x-AnimeSharp.pth"
#   AI_ASSISTANT_UPSCALER="4x_NMKD-Siax_200k.pth"
#   AI_ASSISTANT_UPSCALER="OmniSR_X4_DIV2K.safetensors"
# (Place the .pth/.safetensors in $AI_ASSISTANT_MODELS_DIR/ESRGAN/ first.)
#
# Default: 4x_NMKD-Superscale-SP_178000_G.pth
#AI_ASSISTANT_UPSCALER=""

# --- Models ----------------------------------------------------------------

# Where AI-Assistant's downloaded models live. Stability Matrix users
# typically point this at the shared Models tree so SM and AI-Assistant see
# the same files:
#   AI_ASSISTANT_MODELS_DIR="/Volumes/SSD/Stability Matrix/Data/Models"
#
# Default: <repo>/models
#AI_ASSISTANT_MODELS_DIR=""
